• Please note when registering for classes the maximum amount of credit hours students should enroll in for a 7-week session is 9 credits and for 3-week session is 6 credits.

• Visit www.csmd.edu/academiccalendar for the academic calendar, including registration dates and other important info.

• After you register, it can take up to 24 hours for your financial aid to be applied to courses that are required for your program of study.
